trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event occurs when a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> is added or removed from a managed collection of such lists.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>hendelsen oppstår når en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>legges til eller fjernes fra en forvaltet samling av slike lister.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>

trans-unit.source: This event is not raised when an individual list element changes its value.
trans-unit.target: Denne hendelsen oppstår ikke når et element for individuelle listen endres verdien.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event is generated by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> class when its <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A>, and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Clear%2A> methods are executed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>hendelsen er generert av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService>klasse når den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A>, og <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Clear%2A>metoder kjøres.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Clear%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Remove%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event, the `relatedObject` parameter will always reference the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component> that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> is associated with.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>hendelsen den `relatedObject` parameteren vil alltid referere til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component>som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>er knyttet til.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Component> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>

trans-unit.source: The object that is associated with the collection.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som er knyttet til samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A value that specifies whether a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> has been added or removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir om en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> er lagt til eller fjernes fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The collection of list elements after the action has been applied.
trans-unit.target: Samling av listeelementer etter at handlingen som er brukt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects associated with this event.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekter som er tilknyttet denne hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The retrieved <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> represents the state of the collection after the event, which involved adding or removing an element, has been applied.
trans-unit.target: De hentede <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>representerer tilstanden til samlingen etter at hendelsen, som involvert legge til eller fjerne et element, er brukt.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> that represents the current state of the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> som representerer gjeldende status for samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a flag indicating whether an element has been added or removed from the collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter et flagg som indikerer om et element har lagt til eller fjernes fra samlingen av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Altering the contents of an existing <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> in the collection will not raise a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Endre innholdet i en eksisterende <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>i samlingen kan ikke heve en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>hendelse.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedType"></xref> that indicates the type of change.
Gets the object that that is associated with the collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter objektet som er knyttet til samlingen av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The RelatedObject property enables the programmer to associate an object to an instance of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs> class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen RelatedObject aktiverer i programmer å knytte et objekt til en forekomst av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>klassen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event, the RelatedObject property should always reference the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component?displayProperty=fullName> that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> is associated with.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>hendelsen egenskapen RelatedObject må alltid referere til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Component?displayProperty=fullName>som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>er knyttet til.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Component?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>
